metadata.name: The SunFlower That Grew #1
metadata.description:
In honor of the release of my new song "War Games" I would like to gift the people who have shown up for me with an original line drawing paying homage to this occasion. There are 5 pieces in the collection. 1 main image and 4 color variations. 10 editions of each piece. Thank You for showing up for me. 

With Love,
Scolla
(OG Cool)
